The upside of the second narrative is hopefully persuading Russian invaders to surrender rather than fight this needless war. This would help negate the following potential play.

I worry the first wave of Russian invaders was made up of the less devoted and nationalistic units. Why do this? 1) Thin the ranks of the loyally weakest and 2) Show the growing Russian casualty list to the more fanatical 2nd wave troops to justify upcoming atrocities. This is purely speculation on my part.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Ks86b3f</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[kaiserkevin]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>stagergy</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ImsLNhq</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/flQ0NNa.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ImsLNhq</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[maximilianfragglebottom]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>A message from Anonymous</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/RmNmvio</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Q2y1B37.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HyOJdy4.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zIKUUd9.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/RmNmvio</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[yougotjamed]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Bern still Bernin'</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/tjHs554</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZBUT9CE.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/tjHs554</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[omnifella]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>A moderately sized DK dump of stolen memes for these trying times 649.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/oyEv8xR</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0MG7Oeo.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></s